profiles.name: Barney West
profiles.bio: 47 years old, obese, owns a famous bar Ciacco-I.He was known to be a notorious womaniser who had his eighth divorce a few years back. He is not married right now, but he was spotted at a recent gathering with a well known actress.He lives in his apartment with his dogs, Fluffy, Buckbeak and Hedwig.He also owns a blog site- ‘The 20th Century Philanderer’ - where he keeps publishing articles every fortnight.Barney has had a number of health scares in the past. He has been diagnosed with hypertension, and high levels of triglycerides.
